# Auto-generated by @tanstack/router-plugin at build time. Committing this
# file causes routes to silently 404 when new route files are added but the
# stale committed tree isn't regenerated before deploy — this happened for
# real (admin/settings and other routes were unreachable in production for
# an unknown amount of time before this was caught). Always regenerate via
# `npm run build` or `vite dev`, never hand-edit or commit it.
src/routeTree.gen.ts

